======>  Working Principle
Flex sensors detect finger bending.
ESP32 reads sensor values and identifies gestures.
Corresponding messages are sent to the Blynk application.
Pulse sensor continuously measures heart rate.
DHT11 measures temperature and humidity.
If abnormal health conditions are detected, alerts are generated.
Caregivers can remotely activate the buzzer through the Blynk dashboard.
